---
title: Roasted Mediterranean Veggies and Burrata with Tomato Jam and Polenta
description: Polenta is a tasty alternative to pasta and potatoes. It's made with cornmeal and typically served either creamy, like mashed potatoes, or firm. When cooled it has a sliceable texture and can be baked, fried or even grilled!
